item.title: Post
item.description: First Blog - First Day of New Habits - Half Month into My 1st Dev Job Today is a special day for me. It marks the start of our 5AM Project; The start of our attempt to build better habits and rid of bad habits. We woke up at 5:30 AM. Did our morning routines. Studied what we always find tired of studying at the end of a work day.
